query:
SELECT h.id as hotel_id, h.name as hotel_name, h.linkedDocumentId, d.id as doc_id, d.name as doc_name, d.fileUrl, LENGTH(d.fileUrl) as url_length
FROM hotels h 
INNER JOIN documents d ON h.linkedDocumentId = d.id 
WHERE h.name = 'Vienna Parking'
LIMIT 5;
